# 🧪 POST Invalid Data Test

## 📌 Objective
Test how the API handles invalid input data when creating a user using POST request.

## 📍 Endpoint
POST https://reqres.in/api/users

## 🧪 Test Cases
3 TEST Cases

### ❌ Test 1: Invalid Email Format

Request:
</>JSON
{
  "name": "John",
  "email": "invalid-email",
  "password": "123456"
}
Expected:

400 or 422 status code
Error message "Invalid email format"
User should NOT be created

Actual:

201 Created
User created successfully
API accepts invalid email format

